{"tid":1761521,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"〈唐山大兄〉原唱、「粵曲王子」鄭錦昌逝世，享年78歲。","createTime":"2019-11-29T03:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T19:09:37.000Z","uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"59000efe396566a21f505b6099f9f53b765e6677","tid":1761521,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/upxRSJKoERk/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FupxRSJKoERk%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=ff58937e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大馬資深藝人鄭錦昌逝世，得年78歲。<br />\n<br />\n大馬國寶級資深藝人鄭錦昌今早9時在家中逝世，享年78歲， 噩耗傳出讓人感嘆大馬甘草藝人又走一人。<br />\n<br />\n生於1941年12月22日的鄭錦昌，人稱昌哥，自小習粵曲，聲線美及咬字清，1966年出版第一張個人華語唱片。1969年憑〈鴛鴦江〉在東南亞及香港成名，更獲封「粵曲王子」的美稱。<br />\n<br />\n1973年，與李小龍在香港經典節目《歡樂今宵》同台演出，他所演唱的〈唐山大兄〉流傳至今。<br />\n<br />\n近年來身體抱恙的昌哥，2017年他於香港舉行4場告別演唱會，同年在大馬演藝圈一群好友包括謝玲玲、江夢蕾、李燕萍、林秋燕、陳美娥、林德榮等，也在《鄭錦昌友情友愛演唱會》上向這位優秀的前輩致意，其後鄭錦昌正式退休，結束長達50多年輝煌的演繹與歌唱事業。<br />\n<br />\n光華日報<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kwongwah.com.my/20191129/%E5%A4%A7%E9%A9%AC%E8%B5%84%E6%B7%B1%E8%89%BA%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%91%E9%94%A6%E6%98%8C%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A9%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kwongwah.com.my%2F20191129%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25A9%25AC%25E8%25B5%2584%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E8%2589%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2583%2591%25E9%2594%25A6%25E6%2598%258C%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A9%25E9%2580%259D%25E4%25B8%2596%2F&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=8217dc50\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kwongwah.com.my/20191129/%E5%A4%A7%E9%A9%AC%E8%B5%84%E6%B7%B1%E8%89%BA%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%91%E9%94%A6%E6%98%8C%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A9%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96/</a>"},{"pid":"3c96daa4557f4fd2ff987780af1985aa17530186","tid":1761521,"uid":313584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:39:01.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60e17175daf8328897a0574d29267386dd1d289","tid":176